{"tid":1869793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"強制檢疫？中英街關口 仍有中國人可以自出自入 而不用受強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-02-08T11:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T12:35:55.000Z","uid":187688,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"847758ed99bd19408c22658c01739e795c8364a2","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"又唔洗量體溫，咩檢測都冇，自由出入，完全冇出入境管制，好易奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【沙頭角邊境各區域運作】<br />\n1962年港英政府大幅增加邊境禁區，目的為減少中港邊境活動。雖然2012年特區政府陸續大幅減少禁區範圍，但沙頭角墟一帶維持屬於本港邊境禁區之內。禁區內區域主要分為兩部份：屬於香港境內的禁區（中英街以西）及屬於中國境內的管理區（中英街）。<br />\n<br />\n沙頭角屬於北區區議會沙打選區，現任區議員為民建聯高維基。高維基於2019年區議會選舉以3143票擊敗取得2242票的非建制派對手蔡旭威，成為民建聯唯一的現任北區區議員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TV1RzoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTV1RzoZ.jpg&h=cb7fb256&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39ae463c77a5d785a5c6093e9e4ef8843c9898ae","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"咁大個缺口冇人講 <br />\n疫情隨時由呢個關口爆發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0661500f76f828146b23fee38066b24746632e7","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"全面封關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aefa4361e26732acc0975fdca37863c353ce71d","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"推爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81332d583c0eb87913f9c0fd4023cde0da7fd807","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"有咩理由 呢個關口唔洗 出入境管制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0ab0c6639794793f91208ec1f120812aa58b79","tid":1869793,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/XYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FXYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=8b6342a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FXYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU%2F&h=dcf85b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/XYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU/</a>"},{"pid":"f4101229f4561bd0a112a54c811efb7c5be9bea3","tid":1869793,"uid":187688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0ab0c6639794793f91208ec1f120812aa58b79","tid":1869793,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/XYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FXYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=8b6342a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FXYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU%2F&h=dcf85b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/XYKRU22VXTXJJWDVETCFP7PNKU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"政府早前稱周五（7日）會與居民商討相關安排。在檢疫措施生效前，大批中英街的香港居民急忙執拾行李，舉家返回香港境內等候商討結果，並表明<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對在中英街實行強制檢疫措施</span></strong>。然而，民政署人員及警方晚上約9時到場商討，但在措施生效前都無法提出具體安排，僅向居民稱周一（10日）再議，因此有關安排<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">或</span></strong>照常在中英街實施。<br />\n<br />\n仲傾緊，唔可以留有缺口，全面真封關<img src=\"/